clear_player_role.help: Removes the player role of users not present in the challonge
clear_player_role.users_role_not_removed:
__List of users that kept the role due to a system error:__
%1
clear_player_role.usage:
Usage: `%0clear_player_role $./parameter`

`<remove_player_role>` is `True` by default.
Example: `%0clear_player_role 1 False`
clear_player_role.default:
List of all brackets:
%1
Use `%0clear_player_role $./parameter` to clear the player roles of a bracket.

give_player_role.help: Gives the player role of users not present in the challonge

%1
Use `%0give_player_role $./parameter` to give the player roles of a bracket.

set_schedules_spreadsheet_date_format.usage:
Usage: `%0set_schedules_spreadsheet_date_format $./parameter`

Example: `%0set_schedules_spreadsheet_date_format %d %B`
This flag example corresponds to a string like `01 April`.

For more information about the possible flags, check https://docs.python.org/3/library/datetime.html#strftime-and-strptime-format-codes.
